{"tid":925787,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"口裡說不 身體卻很誠實","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T06:25:57.000Z","uid":8171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9551bf32c41c8b5b2e19e1c1a84a598b8827db9e","tid":925787,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"人類總會犯相同的錯，Samsung 尼日利亞官方 Twitter 在發 Galaxy Note 9 廣告時竟用了 iPhone 來發帖子，並顯示 &ldquo; sent from Twitter for iPhone&rdquo;。這事情被科技評論人 MKBHD 發現，並擷取了圖片。事件曝光後，Samsung 的帖子當然立即刪除了帖子。這種事情已不是首次發生，較早前沙特阿拉伯的 Samsung 官方 Twitter 也曾出現 &ldquo; sent from Twitter for iPhone&rdquo; 的帖子。<br />\n<br />\n其實 Twitter 早就是 Android 手機代言人的陷阱，不時也出 Android 人機代言戈錯用 iPhone 發帖文的事件，不過廠商官方 Twitter 出現如此嚴重的錯誤就真的較少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/samsung-twitter-768x765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Fsamsung-twitter-768x765.jpg&h=f713ca50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9847ea6dfb1b913f3fab7c87fb3318e708bd70bd","tid":925787,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"an狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7951da532ec18d01b096c9a3e9da118adee1771","tid":925787,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"本身無人睇佢 做單咁既新聞收視高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a14abc666e1e4a92f78155152dfa0e66e96e071","tid":925787,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80e8915e5fb086fa9d633adda428944fad7000d3","tid":925787,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bgr.com/2015/06